<div class="breadcrumb"><a href="index.php?index_en">Medic Clean Air</a></div><!--/breadcrumb-->
<a name="jump2" id="jump2"></a><!-- Livedate: 19.07.2010 15:21:30 / Killdate: 16.07.2020 15:21:30 -->
<h1>MedicCleanAir is specialized in:</h1>
<h3>Mobile Air Purification &amp; creation of Isolation Rooms (negative or positive pressure within ½ day)</h3>
<p><img src="picture/upload/image/new-address.png" alt="New Address" width="520" height="177" /></p>


<!-- 
	Livedate: 19.07.2010 15:21:30 / Killdate: 16.07.2020 15:21:30 
//-->


<p><strong>Where needed:</strong></p>
<ul>
    <li>Operating rooms, ICU&rsquo;s, recovery</li>
    <li>Isolation for infectious people (tuberculosis, SARS, pox, flu, etc.)</li>
    <li>Isolation for immune-compromised patients (HIV, oncology, etc.)</li>
    <li>Protection of patients against Aspergillosis (renovation works)</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>When needed:</strong></p>
<ul>
    <li>To upgrade air quality when the usual ventilation systems do not perform as they should do.</li>
    <li>To introduce low-cost / high air quality in new buildings</li>
    <li>To avoid expensive renovation works.</li>
    <li>To immediately create isolation rooms during outbreaks (infectious diseases, Aspergillosis, etc.)</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>How do we create infectious free areas:</strong><br />
By means of HEPA and ULPA filtration.</p>
<p><strong>Important technical details:</strong><br />
Devices are compact, easy to transport, easy to install, only need electricity, low consumption, etc.<br />
No maintenance, only filter change after 12-18 months and when necessary, can be done by usual  staff (no training needed)</p>
<p><strong>What is eliminated:</strong><br />
All airborne infectious agents, including gases and chemical compounds.<br />
Proof:  about 15 different medical/scientific studies from Belgium, Germany, UK, Denmark, Iran, India, Italy, etc.</p>
<p><strong>Contact</strong><br />
MedicCleanAir<br />
Division of Walsberghe nv<br />
Mr. Hendrik Van Passel, managing director<br />
Melkmarkt 35<br />
B-2000 Antwerp &ndash; Belgium<br />
<br />
Phone +32-3-8607060<br />
Fax  +32-3-8607069<br />
<a href="mailto:info@mediccleanair.com">info@mediccleanair.com</a><br />
<a href="http://www.mediccleanair.com">www.mediccleanair.com</a></p></div> <!--/content-mitte-->


